author: Just Jared
title: Chelsea Peretti Is Pregnant, Expecting First Child with Jordan Peele!
text:
Chelsea Peretti and her husband Jordan Peele are expecting a baby!
The 38-year-old Brooklyn Nine-Nine actress and the 37-year-old Key & Peele actor got married back in April 2016 before enjoying a romantic honeymoon in Italy in July.
PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Chelsea Peretti 
Chelsea just announced the exciting pregnancy news today.
“ Beyonce schmonce,” she captioned the Instagram photo below in which she shows off her baby bump in her reflection.
Congrats to Chelsea and Jordan on the upcoming baby!
A photo posted by Chelsea Peretti (@chelsanity) on Feb 4, 2017 at 3:12pm PST
